subproject.description: UN Country Team in cooperation with the Government of Montenegro and the Austrian Embassy in Montenegro to ensure technical, financial and administrative support for building the UN Eco Shared Premises in Montenegro. The UN Eco Shared Premises is conceptualized using efficient, ecological technology and a modern design that will equally satisfy the Government’s commitment to the Ecological State as well as provide the appropriate common premises for five resident UN Agencies in the country.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
